al plane has alone, but which includes the scatter introduced by\nmerging different studies done in different filters by different investigators.\nThis ``fundamental manifold'' fits the structural and kinematic properties of\nspheroids that span a factor of 100 in sigma and 1000 in r_e. (ABRIDGED)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2005 15:12:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2005 21:23:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
