tions of the final scalar field cannot be expressed in terms of the\ndiagonal elements of some non-trivial density-matrix distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2005 15:37:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
